Class Timer.Timing

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    Timer

    private static class Timer.Timing
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a helper class that represents a single measurement. Notice that it is private and, thus, inaccessible to anything outside the Timer class.
